title: Godfall Impressions, PS5 Eve - Kinda Funny Games Daily 11.11.20
description:
Gary Whitta and Greg run through Godfall impressions, talk about the PS5 launch, and more!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:09:00 - Housekeeping
This Friday Andy is going to stream the Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War campaign with his fancy PC to show off Ray Tracing on his Nvidia RTX 3080 (Sponsored By Nvidia) 2-4PM Friday on twitch.tv/kindafunnygames
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Black Jack & Tom Bock
The Roper Report   -
00:12:56 - Sony Exec: Transition from PS4 to PS5 Expected to Take 3 Years - Jordan Oloman @ IGN
00:19:58 - Sony Exec: Transition from PS4 to PS5 Expected to Take 3 Years - Jordan Oloman @ IGN
00:23:30 - The Last of Us 2 and God of War have Dualsense support - Demi Williams @ GamesRadar
00:27:00 - Godfall Early Impressions are up - Paul Tassi @ Forbes
00:31:00 - All Elite Wrestling Announces New Console Game With WWF No Mercy Director Onboard - Joe Skrebels @ IGN
00:37:03 - Ubisoft apologises for ableist description in Assassin's Creed Valhalla - Marie Dealessandri @ GiBiz
00:42:20 - PSA: These ‘Smoking Xbox Series X’ Viral Videos Are Easy To Fake - Paul Tassi @ Forbes
00:47:00 -  Ad  
00:49:20 - Out today
 Reader mail   -
00:52:20 - Family Console issues - Ray Briggs II
00:59:00 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Greg and Tim
